\">• More at the Datastore directory</a></strong><br /><strong>• <a href=\"http://twitter.com/datastore\">Follow us on Twitter</a></strong></p><table>\n      <caption>\n            THE WORLD IN DRUGS USE\n          </caption>\n      <thead>\n        <tr><th class=\"bold left\">COUNTRY (lowest estimate or overall estimate used)</th><th class=\"left\">Opiates, % of pop, adults</th><th class=\"left\">Amphetamines, % of pop, adults</th><th class=\"left\">Cannabis, % of pop, adults</th><th class=\"left\">Cocaine, % of pop adults</th></tr>\n      </thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td class=\"left\">Afghanistan </td><td class=\"left\"> </td><td class=\"left\">3.6 </td><td class=\"\"> </td><td class=\"\"> </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Albania </td><td class=\"left\">0.1 </td><td class=\"left\">1.8 </td><td class=\"left\">0.1 </td><td class=\"left\">0.45 </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Algeria </td><td class=\"left\"> </td><td class=\"left\">5.2 </td><td class=\"\"> </td><td class=\"left\">0.12 </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Angola </td><td class=\"left\">0.1 </td><td class=\"left\">2.1 </td><td class=\"\"> </td><td class=\"left\">0.25 </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Anguilla </td><td class=\"left\"> </td><td class=\"\"> </td><td class=\"\"> </td><td class=\"\"> </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Antigua & Barbuda </td><td class=\"left\">0.1 </td><td class=\"\"> </td><td class=\"\"> </td><td class=\"left\">0.05 </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Argentina </td><td class=\"left\">2.6 </td><td class=\"left\">7.2 </td><td class=\"left\">0.6 </td><td class=\"left\">0.16 </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Armenia </td><td class=\"left\">0.1 </td><td class=\"left\">3.5 </td><td class=\"left\">0.1 </td><td class=\"left\">0.3 </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Australia </td><td class=\"left\">1.9 </td><td class=\"left\">10.6 </td><td class=\"left\">2.7 </td><td class=\"left\">0.4 </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Austria </td><td class=\"left\">0.9 </td><td class=\"left\">3.5 </td